{"tid":2213756,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"教師「被失德」無緣開學　官方清算不斷　","createTime":"2020-09-22T18:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T05:11:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5a216c29f0e2bebecf2ce1de0c51ec83cceafeb6","tid":2213756,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:19:09.000Z","msg":"曾經，教師與學生分析時弊，正常不過；現在，教師就社會事件發聲，叫作「專業失德」。<br />\n<br />\n6.12 金鐘警民衝擊中被催淚彈擊中右眼，視力僅餘 5 % 的教師楊子俊，大半年後遭投訴「荼毒下一代」，不獲任職的拔萃女書院續約；他提前辭職，學生紛表不捨。<br />\n<br />\n另一位楊老師、小學教師楊博文，被指去年「大三罷」期間，在上水迴旋處慢駛，遭警方截查時腳踢警長，被判襲警罪成，一度被還押小欖。今年 7 月，他遭任教的小學解僱； 9 月，楊老師被判囚 9 周，現獲准保釋等候上訴，無緣代表港隊參與沙灘排球國際賽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%B0%E5%AD%B8%E5%B9%B4-%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%A9%E5%BA%8F-%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB-%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%B1%E5%BE%B7-%E7%84%A1%E7%B7%A3%E9%96%8B%E5%AD%B8-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%B8%85%E7%AE%97%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A7%25A9%25E5%25BA%258F-%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E5%25BE%25B7-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B7%25A3%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%25AE%2597%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2596%25B7%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I27zLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=08318d6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A7%25A9%25E5%25BA%258F-%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E5%25BE%25B7-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B7%25A3%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%25AE%2597%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2596%25B7%2F&h=f1dc8e0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%B0%E5%AD%B8%E5%B9%B4-%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%A9%E5%BA%8F-%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB-%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%B1%E5%BE%B7-%E7%84%A1%E7%B7%A3%E9%96%8B%E5%AD%B8-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%B8%85%E7%AE%97%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7/</a>"},{"pid":"25572e81b9f7cd1ca547d14acdf4c4c07839ac0f","tid":2213756,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:19:54.000Z","msg":"有不願具名的中學教師向《立場》透露，因為他在通識課堂上播了兩集鏗鏘集，被一位家長控訴「妖言惑眾」、「洗學生腦」，他終被高層召見，說了兩句，家長沒再追究。老師形容自己幸運，算是「清算旋渦」中的倖存者，因為這一年，被投訴、被施壓、被譴責、被警告的教師，多不勝數。<br />\n<br />\n2020 年 5 月，教育局公開專上院校及中小學教職員因社會事件被捕的數字，共有 110 名。一個月後，教育局再公布過去一年共接獲 222 宗教師在社會事件中涉嫌專業失當投訴，這些被指「失德」的老師，是高官口中的「害群之馬」。"},{"pid":"caa2a45d39b4e2f8500ddaf8fd4b099c450d4074","tid":2213756,"uid":115579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:47:24.000Z","msg":"鏗鏘集擺到明中立持平都叫洗腦"},{"pid":"f709898594f93e92e5b4671dd712bd3a16b2a12e","tid":2213756,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bbf23a5442f512c39e207c3e823639939c6ae65","tid":2213756,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:56:36.000Z","msg":"投訴返學校啦屌"},{"pid":"10285daaecdafb26188d84da7593db9d0053dafe","tid":2213756,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f709898594f93e92e5b4671dd712bd3a16b2a12e","tid":2213756,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T19:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"